    "description_long": "This is a modern, rectangular wooden cabinet with a natural wood grain finish on the top, sides, and legs. The front features three large, flat white doors with no visible handles, giving it a minimalist appearance. The back and sides are plain, showcasing the wood texture. When the doors are open, the interior reveals three compartments, each with a green drawer above and an open shelf below. The drawers have small metallic knobs for pulling. The cabinet stands on four angled wooden legs, providing stability and a mid-century modern aesthetic.",
